name: J'adore Eau de Parfum
description: An iconic floral bouquet, subtly balanced and enriched with notes of fruity sweetness and a woody base.

name: J'adore L'Or
description: An opulent, intense interpretation of J'adore, blending Grandiflorum Jasmine and May Rose absolutes.

name: J'adore Infinissime
description: An endless explosion of freed flowers, with a new, sensual Tuberose note.
notes_middle: Centifolia Rose, Jasmine Sambac, Tuberose, Ylang-Ylang

name: J'adore Parfum d'eau
description: A pioneering alcohol-free floral fragrance, a new expression of J'adore's iconic bouquet.

name: J'adore in Joy
description: A scent that literally smells of joy, with a fresh, salty floral composition.

name: J'adore L'Absolu
description: A more concentrated and intense version of J'adore, emphasizing floral absolutes.

name: Sauvage Eau de Toilette
description: A radically fresh composition that is raw and noble, inspired by wide-open spaces.

name: Sauvage Eau de Parfum
description: A more intense and sensual take on Sauvage, enriched with spicy and vanilla notes.

name: Sauvage Parfum
description: The purest and most concentrated expression of Sauvage, with an extreme freshness.

name: Sauvage Elixir
description: An exceptionally concentrated fragrance, like a fine liquor, with a powerful, fresh, and woody trail.

name: Sauvage Eau Forte

name: Sauvage Very Cool Spray
description: A nomadic, irresistible, and informal spray version of Sauvage, easy to apply.

name: Miss Dior Eau de Parfum
description: The emblematic couture fragrance, a thousand flowers in a vibrant olfactory embrace.

name: Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet
description: A fresh and sparkling floral composition, like a spring dress embroidered with a thousand flowers.

name: Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming
description: A sparkling and colorful floral delight, an armful of fresh, delicious berries.

name: Miss Dior Rose N'Roses

name: Miss Dior Parfum (2024)

name: Miss Dior Chérie (older iterations)
price: N/A (Discontinued, varies greatly on resale market)
description: The original Miss Dior Chérie, known for its gourmand chypre notes and iconic popcorn accord. (Discontinued)

name: Dior Homme Eau de Toilette
description: A modern classic for men, characterized by its powdery iris note and elegant woody facets.

name: Dior Homme Eau de Parfum
description: A sensual and refined version of Dior Homme, with a stronger presence of leather and iris.

name: Dior Homme Intense
description: A powerful and sophisticated evening fragrance, renowned for its intense iris, amber, and vanilla notes.

name: Dior Homme Sport
description: A dynamic and elegant fragrance, combining citrus freshness with spicy and woody accords.

name: Dior Homme Cologne
description: A vibrant and radiant fragrance built around a fresh and elegant floral accord.

name: Dior Homme Parfum
description: The ultimate expression of Dior Homme, a concentrated and luxurious blend of iris, leather, and wood.

name: Poison
description: An intoxicating and legendary oriental fragrance, a true icon of seduction.

name: Hypnotic Poison
description: A mysterious and captivating oriental fragrance, an amber-vanilla seduction.

name: Pure Poison
description: A luminous and captivating white floral, pure and seductive, an elixir of light.

name: Midnight Poison
price: N/A (Discontinued, very high on resale market)
description: A dark, mysterious, and elegant chypre-rose fragrance with patchouli and amber. (Discontinued)

name: Poison Girl
description: A delicious and seductive oriental-gourmand fragrance for a modern, free woman.
notes_middle: Damask Rose, Grasses Rose, Orange Blossom
notes_base: Tonka Bean, Vanilla, Almond, Sandalwood, Cashmeran

name: Tendre Poison
price: N/A (Discontinued, rare and expensive on resale market)
description: A lighter, greener, and more floral version of the original Poison, with a fresh elegance. (Discontinued)
notes_middle: Tuberose, Honey, Orange Blossom, Freesia, Rose

name: Fahrenheit
description: A unique and daring fragrance, a woody-floral-musk with an iconic violet and leather accord.

name: Fahrenheit 32
description: A clean, icy, and luminous oriental-woody fragrance, a surprising departure from the original. (Discontinued)

name: Eau Sauvage Eau de Toilette
description: The first men's fragrance by Dior, an iconic, timeless, and revolutionary fresh citrus chypre.

name: Eau Sauvage Eau de Parfum
description: A contemporary interpretation of the original, deeper and more intense with a prominent myrrh note.

name: Eau Sauvage Cologne

name: Eau Sauvage Fraîcheur Cuir
description: A limited edition with a fresh leather accord, adding a new dimension to Eau Sauvage. (Discontinued)

name: Eau Sauvage Extrême

name: Diorissimo

name: Dune

notes_base: Sandalwood, Amber, Vanilla, Patchouli, Benzoin, Musk

name: Addict
description: A captivating and sensual oriental floral fragrance, powerful and seductive.

name: Joy by Dior

description: A noble and sophisticated amber fragrance, a warm encounter between an opulent amber and the Turkish rose.

name: Gris Dior

description: A sunny fragrance inspired by the French Riviera, evoking the scent of the Mediterranean sea and pine trees.

name: Spice Blend

name: Rose Kabuki

name: Sakura

name: Lucky

name: New Look 2024
description: A new interpretation celebrating the iconic 'New Look', likely with a fresh, elegant, and timeless appeal.

name: Dioriviera
description: A sunny and captivating fragrance, evoking the charm of the French Riviera with fig and rose.

name: Jasmin des Anges

name: Cologne Blanche (re-released)
description: A soft and powdery oriental, combining almond and orange blossom with a refined amber base. Re-released in 2024 as part of the new collection structure.

name: Eau Noire (re-released)
description: A dark and aromatic fragrance with notes of lavender, coffee, and licorice. Re-released in 2024 as part of the new collection structure.

name: Santal Noir
description: A sensual and mysterious woody fragrance, blending the creamy warmth of sandalwood with amber and rose.
